overview: The user wanted to elevate the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which they felt lacked a refined aesthetic. The agent
  initiated a detailed review of the app's existing styling, covering global
  CSS, layout, and individual components. Based on this analysis, a new, calming
  sleep-themed color palette was introduced, featuring deep indigos, purples,
  and teal accents. Significant improvements were made to the main questionnaire
  form, including decorative background elements, a redesigned progress bar, and
  a subtle star pattern on card headers. The welcome (IntroSection) and report
  sections were also overhauled with new layouts, feature cards, and consistent
  styling. Form components like checkboxes, radio buttons, and sliders were
  refined for a more polished look and feel. The agent systematically applied
  these changes, ensuring a cohesive and professional aesthetic throughout the
  application, and confirmed the visual enhancements by reviewing the app in the
  browser.
